{"tid":1215930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中資銀行打比我媽咪","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:10:29.000Z","uid":139079,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c03c9432b1e4e19b2319400c51c46ba968d97e5","tid":1215930,"uid":139079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"我尋晚發夢 夢到媽咪同我講左件咁既事<br />\n<br />\n咁我媽要幫我爸爸間公司做小幫手（小生意黎）因為爸爸最近身體差，就想加番媽咪個名等佢都可以簽支票<br />\n<br />\n咁就係尋日，南洋銀行一位跟開佢地既人就打比我媽咪，問佢係咪有搞過政治？<br />\n<br />\n我媽咪就呆左：下？緊係無啦！無無無！<br />\n<br />\n拿，我媽咪正職就家庭主婦黎，掛名幫下老豆手姐，又點會搞到政治？<br />\n<br />\n對方就話：啊，咁可能有人同你同名啦，無野啦咁，ok 架啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係咁。原來佢打黎就係問一句，對方就收左線啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個夢真係好怪。大家點睇？"},{"pid":"ce42f7c7c183925456c6cbc86727dd5c2df00ac5","tid":1215930,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"樓主係林奠個仔？"},{"pid":"e7f7bd84eb465699b4f81c7a9a25b46371259196","tid":1215930,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"南洋 = 集友 = 中銀"},{"pid":"29f17c58bd11a75daf15727051f26abfb63728cb","tid":1215930,"uid":139079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f7bd84eb465699b4f81c7a9a25b46371259196","tid":1215930,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"南洋 = 集友 = 中銀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"我知呀，不過佢突然打電話黎問一句咁算點。仲要係尋日。"},{"pid":"69754f49e829df205bc1e4b7ed2c9530a3ced868","tid":1215930,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:01:06.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"d1081fd6025f00acfd786e25343344847e5106e9","tid":1215930,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"扮銀行職員是常識吧"},{"pid":"cd5c7ac6051ce2e072f7e5bb192079ca4673b9f4","tid":1215930,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"PEP?"},{"pid":"a853b9b541269